Fighting monsters online...

00:16:38.600 --> 00:16:39.679
...no wonder he got killed.

00:16:40.320 --> 00:16:41.639
Don't say that.

00:16:42.720 --> 00:16:44.279
Little Wu meant well.

00:16:44.960 --> 00:16:46.139
He just wanted me to quickly...

00:16:46.139 --> 00:16:47.879
...fit into the young people's world.

00:16:48.519 --> 00:16:50.200
Why are you still siding with him?

00:16:50.759 --> 00:16:52.320
You can fit in with them?

00:16:52.600 --> 00:16:54.120
That Bear League...

00:16:54.120 --> 00:16:55.860
...everyone's tougher than a bear.

00:16:56.480 --> 00:16:58.320
Go get some snacks, hurry up.

00:16:59.000 --> 00:16:59.639
Right.

00:16:59.639 --> 00:16:59.960
Right away.

00:16:59.960 --> 00:17:00.759
Right away!

00:17:01.519 --> 00:17:02.879
Isn't life just great?

00:17:02.879 --> 00:17:03.139
Dad.

00:17:03.139 --> 00:17:03.519
Dad.

