Through analysis...

00:17:23.500 --> 00:17:24.619
...step by step...

00:17:24.619 --> 00:17:26.339
...you find the killer.

00:17:26.339 --> 00:17:27.579
Now that I've said that...

00:17:27.579 --> 00:17:28.880
...you get the idea, right?

00:17:29.140 --> 00:17:30.180
Get what idea?

00:17:30.779 --> 00:17:32.059
I'm still totally lost.

00:17:32.779 --> 00:17:33.980
Anyway, one thing is for sure.

00:17:34.819 --> 00:17:36.019
I remember this clearly.

00:17:36.660 --> 00:17:37.799
I am not the murderer.

00:17:38.859 --> 00:17:39.980
Sir...

00:17:40.420 --> 00:17:42.819
...don't spoil too much information.

00:17:43.140 --> 00:17:45.059
But I'm really not the murderer!

00:17:46.140 --> 00:17:46.839
Then...

00:17:47.279 --> 00:17:48.079
...look...

00:17:49.000 --> 00:17:50.119
...which of them is the murderer?

