Dad, what about me?

00:17:53.519 --> 00:17:54.079
What about me?

00:17:54.079 --> 00:17:54.720
You...

00:17:55.880 --> 00:17:57.359
...don't look innocent either.

00:17:58.960 --> 00:17:59.880
Why do you all look...

00:17:59.880 --> 00:18:01.079
...like murderers to me?

00:18:02.559 --> 00:18:03.200
Every single one.

00:18:03.200 --> 00:18:04.380
How is that possible?

00:18:08.440 --> 00:18:09.200
I'm not going in

